    "In addition, these applications align with broader educational imperatives frequently discussed in scholarly literature.",
    "Through a thematic analysis of challenges reported in 37 empirical studies, this section explores critical barriers to integrating GenAI into higher education practices.",
    "Twentyfive distinct codes were grouped into four areas: (1) Technical, Usability, and Scalability; (2) Quality and Ethical Concerns; (3) Pedagogical Challenges; and (4) AI Literacy and Dependency.",
